@startuml
title Последовательность работы replay-микросервиса

participant "Prepared node file" as File
participant "Replay Engine" as Replay
participant "State Manager" as State
participant "Inference Engine" as Infer
participant "Threshold Registry" as Thr
participant "Prometheus Exporter" as Exp
participant "Prometheus" as Prom
participant "Grafana" as Graf

File -> Replay: чтение очередной точки узла
Replay -> State: обновление позиции и буфера окна
State -> Infer: передача окна CPU/voltage
Infer -> Thr: получение per-node threshold
Infer -> Infer: вычисление score_cpu, score_voltage,\nscore_combined
Infer -> Exp: публикация score и anomaly_flag
Exp -> Prom: экспорт /metrics
Prom -> Graf: предоставление метрик для визуализации
@enduml